name: Henries Winner!
description: Stripey Cats are proud to announce that they picked up the award for Best Childrens' Range at The Henries Awards, for my wobbly eyed animal cards. The Henries Awards 2013 took place in the glittering surroundings of the prestigious Lancaster London Hotel on October 10 to celebrate the immense creativity in the UK greeting card industry. Over 600 greeting card industry publishers and retailers attended the event to honour the industry’s best greeting card ranges. Over 14,000 greeting cards were entered into The Henries year, judged by a panel of 40 prestigious retailers, including buyers from John Lewis, Paperchase, Clintons, Tesco, Waterstones and a host of leading independents. Comedian Tom Stade, brought his own unique brand of humour to the event as host this year. Warren Lomax, joint owner of The Henries awards commented: “What a fantastic night for the UK greeting card industry. It is great to shine the spotlight on the fantastic creativity, innovation and design within the greeting card industry.” See more at www.thehenriesawards.co.uk

name: Framed Prints
description: Beautiful framed prints featuring your favourite Stripey Cats animals. Great for birthday, christening, Christmas or Easter gifts for that special girl or boy. Your children and their friends will love to have their favourite Stripey Cats characters up on the wall of the nursery, playroom or bedroom. Choose from 4 different colourways and a whole host of animals to make the perfect gift. Can be hung up (hanging items included) or stood on its side. The Frames are wrapped in tissue paper and comes packaged in its own gift box. Made from: A 7 x 7 inch matt white frame with a high quality animal print with wibbly wobbly eyes and a glass pane front. Features a lovely bespoke cut mount. Dimensions: Frame size 18 x 18cms (7 x 7 inch) and 19mm deep. Postage: Free postage to any UK address! Discount offer: Select 3 or more frames and add discount code Framed at checkout to receive 20% off your order.

name: Personalised Clock
description: TELLING the time can be lots of fun with these cute and quirky personalised framed clocks featuring your favourite Stripey Cats animals. Just give us the name of the lucky recipient, choose a preferred googly-eyed animal and colourway and we'll do the rest. Great for birthday, christening, christmas or easter gifts for that special girl or boy. Your children and their friends will love to have their own personalised time piece for the wall of the nursery, playroom or bedroom. Choose from 5 different colour ways and a whole host of animals to make the perfect personalised gift. Can be hung up (hanging item included) or stood on its side. Clock comes packaged in its own gift box. Available Colours: blue, pink, green, yellow, lilac How to Personalise: email name and colour choice to stripeycats@icloud.com Dimensions: 9 x 7 x 1.5 inch matt white frame, with a wobbly eyed high quality print and a glass pane front. Features: A high quality silent non whirring clock mechanism, requires 1 AA battery (not included) Postage: Free postage to the UK.
